  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个OTT视频平台的用户状态流转图。核心场景是：用户先连接到平台，然后可以选择创建房间或者加入房间，最后开始看视频。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那用户初始状态是从哪里开始？是直接从连接OTT开始，还是需要先有一个未登录的初始状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Connect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "直接从连接开始就行，用起始节点表示。连接成功后，用户有两个并行选择：创建房间或者加入已有房间。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把起始节点连到Connect，然后从Connect分出两条线到CreateRoom和JoinRoom。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对了，还有一个细节：创建房间之后，创建者自动加入该房间，所以CreateRoom也要能流转到JoinRoom。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上CreateRoom到JoinRoom的连线。那用户进入房间后，下一步就是使用OTT看视频了对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，JoinRoom之后就是UseOTT，用户开始观看视频。视频观看结束，整个流程就终止了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
